    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>将荒芜星球改造成繁荣家园</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《备用计划：家园》（Plan B: Terraform）是一款宁静而富有思考性的科幻模拟游戏，背景设定在未来——人类为了生存不得不将目光投向地球之外。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的使命：将一颗新发现的星球改造成适合人类居住的家园。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在超过百万个六边形格子的广阔地形上探索，并掌控完整的生态系统模拟 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1894430/extras/548757628123a96e8f7140e37238feec.poster.avif?t=1756796137\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1894430/extras/548757628123a96e8f7140e37238feec.webm?t=1756796137\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1894430/extras/548757628123a96e8f7140e37238feec.mp4?t=1756796137\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>塑造气候、水源与生命</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过建造温室气体发电厂来提升全球气温，解锁地下冰层以形成奔流的河川与浩瀚的海洋，并让植被重返大地。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将见证动态天气系统：蒸发、风向与降雨的循环。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >最终，把一片死寂变为充满森林、河流与海洋的生机世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1894430/extras/d994501f6010cd8eeacee7e2fcef414a.poster.avif?t=1756796137\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1894430/extras/d994501f6010cd8eeacee7e2fcef414a.webm?t=1756796137\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1894430/extras/d994501f6010cd8eeacee7e2fcef414a.mp4?t=1756796137\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>建立供应链，发展城市</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >开采矿物、制造物资，并用卡车、火车、无人机和船舶运输。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建立自动化供应线路以支撑不断扩张的城市，将零星的前哨站发展成数百万人的繁华都市。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一次人口飞跃，都取决于你是否能妥善管理物流，优化基础设施，并维持高效丝滑的自动化运转。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1894430/extras/76471c8ac575d79ceb03e9edbfa32880.poster.avif?t=1756796137\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1894430/extras/76471c8ac575d79ceb03e9edbfa32880.webm?t=1756796137\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1894430/extras/76471c8ac575d79ceb03e9edbfa32880.mp4?t=1756796137\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1894430/extras/227e18c74683a6744bcad9d436a5aae8.poster.avif?t=1756796137\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1894430/extras/227e18c74683a6744bcad9d436a5aae8.webm?t=1756796137\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1894430/extras/227e18c74683a6744bcad9d436a5aae8.mp4?t=1756796137\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
